Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可以!  这个可以!  中啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.30,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\bord0\c&H58565E&\pos(267.067,434.533)}转推
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:49.80,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\bord0\c&H58565E&\pos(275.6,613.733)}转推
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  你是太着急了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉…你还要拍杂志照的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,茜  你讨厌我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你坚强又温柔  我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我也喜欢努力又认真的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我不生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这个视频在24小时内达成了7万4千的转发量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在改变了黑川茜形象的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,更稳固了《现恋》不可动摇的人气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.35,ONSCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\frz270\fs40\p1\pos(395,2)\fad(840,0)}m 0 0 l -115 0 l -115 450 l 0 450
